sentences.english: Unless your scuba diving equipment is up to standard, do not use it.
sentences.chinese: 如果你的水肺潛泳設備不合標準，就不要使用它。

sentences.english: The balloonist liked to deep sea dive as a hobby.
sentences.chinese: 該名氣球駕駛員喜歡把深海潛泳當做嗜好。

sentences.english: I heard you are now practicing underwater swimming, aren't you?
sentences.chinese: 聽說我在練習學潛泳，對嗎？

sentences.english: He will also be on hand for snorkel tuition and safaris.
sentences.chinese: 他還將在手潛泳學費和狩獵。

sentences.english: I go swimming in summer almost every day.
sentences.chinese: 炎天我險些天天去潛泳。

sentences.english: The SeaQuest ADV offers you the chance to dive the very best of the Outer Barrier Reef in absolute comfort and style.
sentences.chinese: 她讓您以最舒適和時尚的方式潛泳在外大堡礁最佳處。
